  <entry>
    <title>数组</title>
    <link href="/2022/09/12/%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84/"/>
    <url>/2022/09/12/%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="209-长度最小的子数组"><a href="#209-长度最小的子数组" class="headerlink" title="209.长度最小的子数组"></a>209.长度最小的子数组</h1><p>给定一个含有 n 个正整数的数组和一个正整数 target 。</p><p>找出该数组中满足其和 ≥ target 的长度最小的 连续子数组 [numsl, numsl+1, …, numsr-1, numsr] ，并返回其长度。如果不存在符合条件的子数组，返回 0 。</p><p>示例1：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">输入：target = 7, nums = [2,3,1,2,4,3]<br>输出：2<br>解释：子数组 [4,3] 是该条件下的长度最小的子数组。<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>示例2：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">输入：target = 4, nums = [1,4,4]<br>输出：1<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>示例3：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell">输入：target = 11, nums = [1,1,1,1,1,1,1,1]<br>输出：0<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>暴力解法是两个for循环，然后不断的寻找符合条件的子序列，时间复杂度很明显是O(n^2)。 这里我们采用<em><strong>滑动窗口</strong></em>的解法：</p><h3 id="滑动窗口"><a href="#滑动窗口" class="headerlink" title="滑动窗口"></a>滑动窗口</h3><p>在暴力的方法中，我们使用两个for循环，一个控制子数组的起始位置，一个控制子数组的终止位置，在滑动窗口的方法中，我们采用一个for循环来表示子数组的终止位置</p><p><a href="https://cloudimge.com/image/5Riv3"><img src="https://c2.im5i.com/2022/09/12/5Riv3.gif" alt="5Riv3.gif"></a></p><p>注意以下三点：</p><blockquote><p>滑动窗口即为满足其和 ≥ s的长度最小的连续子数组。 </p><p>窗口的起始位置如何移动：如果当前窗口的值大于s了，窗口就要向前移动了（也就是该缩小了）。 </p><p>窗口的结束位置如何移动：窗口的结束位置就是遍历数组的指针，也就是for循环里的索引。 </p></blockquote><p>具体代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://c2.im5i.com/2022/09/12/5RmUy.png" alt="5RmUy.png"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <categories>
      
      <category>算法</category>
      
    </categories>
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>vue笔记</title>
    <link href="/2022/09/12/vue%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <url>/2022/09/12/vue%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一、初始化"><a href="#一、初始化" class="headerlink" title="一、初始化"></a>一、初始化</h1><h3 id="1-引入第一个vue程序："><a href="#1-引入第一个vue程序：" class="headerlink" title="1.引入第一个vue程序："></a>1.引入第一个vue程序：</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html"><span class="hljs-meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="hljs-keyword">html</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">html</span> <span class="hljs-attr">lang</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;en&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">head</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">meta</span> <span class="hljs-attr">charset</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;UTF-8&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">meta</span> <span class="hljs-attr">http-equiv</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;X-UA-Compatible&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">content</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;IE=edge&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">meta</span> <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;viewport&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">content</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">title</span>&gt;</span>Document<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">title</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">script</span> <span class="hljs-attr">src</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;../vue.js/vue.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">head</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">body</span>&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-comment">&lt;!-- 准备vue容器 --&gt;</span><br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">div</span> <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;app&quot;</span>&gt;</span>&#123;&#123;message&#125;&#125;<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">div</span>&gt;</span> //准备好⼀个装载数据的容器<br>    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><span class="language-javascript"></span><br><span class="language-javascript">        <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> app = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Vue</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            <span class="hljs-attr">el</span>:<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;#app&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-comment">// ⽤于指定当前vue实例为哪个容器使⽤，值为css选择器字符串</span></span><br><span class="language-javascript">            <span class="hljs-attr">data</span>: &#123;    <span class="hljs-comment">// ⽤于储存数据，数据供el指定的容器使⽤</span></span><br><span class="language-javascript">                <span class="hljs-attr">message</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Hello world!&#x27;</span>,</span><br><span class="language-javascript">            &#125;,</span><br><span class="language-javascript">        &#125;);</span><br><span class="language-javascript">    </span><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">script</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">body</span>&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">html</span>&gt;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>注意事项：</p><ul><li>一个vue实例只能接管一个容器</li><li>插值语法可以读取到data内的所有属性</li><li>data中数据发生变化，在容器内用到的数据会自动更新</li></ul></blockquote><h3 id="2-vue的模板语法："><a href="#2-vue的模板语法：" class="headerlink" title="2.vue的模板语法："></a>2.vue的模板语法：</h3><p>插值语法：如前所述</p><p>指令语法：⽤在标签的解析（标签属性，标签体内容，绑定事件等） ，vue的指令语法形式为v-bind;</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js"><span class="hljs-comment">// 解析标签属性：v-bind</span><br>v-<span class="hljs-attr">bind</span>:href=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;url&#x27;</span><br>:href=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;url&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-comment">// 简写模式</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-vue中的双向数据绑定"><a href="#3-vue中的双向数据绑定" class="headerlink" title="3.vue中的双向数据绑定"></a>3.vue中的双向数据绑定</h3><p>单向数据绑定：只能从data流向页面</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html">// 通过v-bind实现单项数据绑定<br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;text&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">:value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;name&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>双向数据绑定 ：不仅可以从data流向⻚⾯，也能从⻚⾯表单元素（输⼊元素）流向data </p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs html">// 通过v-model实现双项数据绑定<br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;text&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">v-model:value</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;name&quot;</span> /&gt;</span><br><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span> <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;text&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-attr">v-model</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;name&quot;</span> /&gt;</span> // 简写<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-MVVM模型在Vue中的使⽤"><a href="#4-MVVM模型在Vue中的使⽤" class="headerlink" title="4.MVVM模型在Vue中的使⽤"></a>4.MVVM模型在Vue中的使⽤</h3><p><img src="https://c2.im5i.com/2022/09/12/59X2G.png" alt="59X2G.png"></p><p>M：Model（模型） 对应data的数据 </p><p>V：View（视图） 模板==&gt;⻚⾯ </p><p>VM：ViewModel（视图模型） Vue实例对象 </p><h3 id="5-Vue中的数据代理"><a href="#5-Vue中的数据代理" class="headerlink" title="5.Vue中的数据代理"></a>5.Vue中的数据代理</h3><p>即通过⼀个对象代理另⼀个对象属性的读写 ，原理如下：</p><figure class="highlight h"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs h">Object.defineProperty(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;⽬标对象&#x27;</span>, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;代理属性&#x27;</span>, &#123;<br> get() &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// getter 当读取’⽬标对象‘的’代理属性‘时，get函数/getter就会被调⽤，且返回代理属性的值</span><br> <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> xxx; <br> &#125;,<br> <span class="hljs-built_in">set</span>(value) &#123; <span class="hljs-comment">// setter 当修改’⽬标对象‘的’代理属性‘时，set函数/setter就会被调⽤，且收到修改的值</span><br> xxx;<br> &#125;,<br>&#125;);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>例子：</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js"><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> obj1 = &#123;<br><span class="hljs-attr">a</span>: <span class="hljs-number">111</span>,<br>&#125;;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> obj2 = &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-attr">b</span>: <span class="hljs-number">222</span>,<br>&#125;;<br><span class="hljs-title class_">Object</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">defineProperty</span>(obj2, <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>, &#123;<br><span class="hljs-title function_">get</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>) &#123;<br> <span class="hljs-variable language_">console</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">log</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;obj2被读取了&#x27;</span>);<br> <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> obj1.<span class="hljs-property">a</span>;<br> &#125;,<br> <span class="hljs-title function_">set</span>(<span class="hljs-params">value</span>) &#123;<br> <span class="hljs-variable language_">console</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">log</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;obj2被修改了&#x27;</span>);<br> obj1.<span class="hljs-property">a</span> = value;<br> &#125;,<br>&#125;);<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>使用：</p><p>通过vm对象代理 data/_data 中属性的读写，能更加⽅便的读写vue中data的数据 </p><p>通过 Object.defineProperty() 把 data 中的属性添加到vm对象上，使得每个属性都有setter/getter </p></blockquote><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs js"><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> vm = <span class="hljs-keyword">new</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Vue</span>(&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-attr">el</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;#app&#x27;</span>,<br>        <span class="hljs-attr">data</span>: &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;李阳&#x27;</span>,<br>        &#125;,<br>    &#125;);<br>    <span class="hljs-variable language_">console</span>.<span class="hljs-title function_">log</span>(vm);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
